    Page: 321-322
  Source:
    Title: Man's Quest for God
By: Abraham Joshua Heschel
Format: verse
---
The world is not a vacuum.
Either we make it an altar for God
or it is invaded by demons.

There can be no neutrality.
Either we are ministers of the sacred
or slaves of evil.
